OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1780589464
OL,3,CTeenager has leg amputated after
OL,4,Cstabbing at Barry Island
OL,6,FHowever, police have now confirmed he
OL,7,Fhas since had to undergo a life-
OL,8,Fchanging leg amputation and has been
OL,9,Fsubject to critical care at the
OL,10,FUniversity Hospital of Wales, Cardiff.
OL,12,FDetective Inspector Sarah Lee, from
OL,13,FSouth Wales Police, said: "The extent
OL,14,Fand seriousness of the injury
OL,15,Fsustained by the teenage victim is
OL,16,Fabsolutely devastating.
OL,18,F"Understandably his family are
OL,19,Fdistraught, and they have been
OL,20,Fassigned a specially trained family
OL,21,Fliaison officer for additional support.
OL,26,@uD@[OUzD@AOU
