OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1780589464
OL,3,CTeenager has leg amputated after
OL,4,Cstabbing at Barry Island
OL,6,F"Our investigation, which includes
OL,7,Fexamining hundreds of hours of CCTV
OL,8,Ffootage and tracing witnesses, is
OL,9,Fcontinuing.
OL,11,F"An 18-year-old man from Riverside,
OL,12,FCardiff, who was arrested on the day
OL,13,Fof the incident on suspicion of
OL,14,Fwounding with intent, remains on bail
OL,15,Fpending further enquiries.
OL,17,F"We urge witnesses or anyone with
OL,18,Finformation to please contact South
OL,19,FWales Police or Crimestoppers
OL,20,Fanonymously."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU|D@MO]
